caption.text:
Hear me out! ⬇️

🕐 All great things take time! Speaking from experience, building a great portfolio that will secure you partnerships and deals won’t happen overnight.

💸 You might be seeing other UGC creators seemingly build a portfolio in a day and get paid the next, but the reality is, they probably already had those pics and vids ready to go.

😖 Be picky when making your portfolio! Take your time, and make sure it’s a reflection of your talents, niche, and personality! Especially as a small creator, the only way brands will get to know you is through your portfolio.

Hard work always pays off! Take your time, and remember, slow and steady always wins the race 🤍
